<D>__{we picked up a castaway found him in the water he'd been drifting for days.}
<C>__{lumpy}
<D>__{his ship had run aground on an island, way west of sumatra. an island hidden in fog. he spoke of a huge wall, built so long ago no one knew who had made it ... a wall a hundred foot high ... as strong today as it was, ages ago.}
<C>__{preston}
<D>__{why did they build the wall?}
